Package: bc-duplicate
Architecture: amd64
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
         ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: Parallel duplicate-file finder
 Walks directory trees and reports groups of identical files using a
 size -> partial-hash -> full-hash pipeline. Hashes with xxh3 by
 default (or xxh128 / SHA-256 on demand), with batched I/O via
 io_uring when available. Hardlinks, hidden files, symlinks and
 pseudo-filesystems (/proc, /sys, /dev, ...) are skipped by default.
 .
 Provides 'scan' and 'summary' subcommands and JSON output suitable
 for downstream consumers (e.g. bc-vigil).
